# Linting & Formatting Rules

- **ESLint**: Extends `@raycast`. Run `npm run lint` / `npm run fix-lint`.
- **Prettier**: Respect `.prettierrc` (printWidth 120, semi true, double quotes). Do not override per-file.
- **Indentation**: Preserve existing indentation characters and width. Do not mix spaces/tabs.
- **Imports**: Keep ordering minimal; no unused imports or variables.
- **No reformat churn**: Only change lines you edit; avoid mass reformatting.